    <p>
      5.Draw and fill in the table like the one shown below.
    </p>
    <table>
      <title></title>
      <tabular halign="left" top="medium" bottom="medium" left="medium" right="medium">
        <row header="yes">
          <cell>Object</cell>
          <cell> Circumfrence (C)</cell>
          <cell>Diameter (d)</cell>
          <cell>circumfrence <m>\div</m> diameter <m>(\frac{C}{d})</m></cell>
          
        </row>
        <row >
          <cell></cell>
          <cell></cell>
